oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Leonard family picnic
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of members of the Leonard family gathered for a picnic. Mrs. Griffith Leonard and her son Samuel J. Leonard are among the people pictured. Many of the women are holding fans and buggies are parked behind the family.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Group portraits; Families; Picnics; Fans (Accessories)
